data.description: Drastically reduced for immediate sale ! Excellent location ! Well maintained building, Apartment with excellent layout 2 large bedrooms with 2 full bathrooms (split bedrooms) many closets and a super spacious walking closet in the master Bedroom . Super private balcony with a small view of the intercoastal. Small and cozy building one block from the beach. Physically the apartment looks much larger than the square footage reflected in the tax roll. All pieces are spacious Very bright with sliding glass windows and doors, all with hurricane shutters.
